Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Add /pitch/sleep investor facade + PITCH_MODE nav rewrite

- New hardcoded "Quiet Climb" facade at /pitch/sleep, fully isolated from the real /sleep dashboard (no Supabase, no useTheme, no shared state).
- src/lib/pitchMode.ts with a single PITCH_MODE flag and a pitchHref() helper that silently rewrites known real routes to their /pitch/* counterparts. Flip one boolean to toggle between investor-demo nav and real-app nav.
- Wire pitchHref() into the home grid card links (SandboxHome) and the hamburger menu (SavyMobileMenu). Both nav surfaces now route Sleep to /pitch/sleep while PITCH_MODE is true.
- Real /sleep dashboard still reachable by direct URL (backdoor for day-to-day use).

Made-with: Cursor
